subSections.text:
{{ja-noun|ほぞ}}

# {{alternative spelling of|lang=ja|臍||a [[navel]]; a [[protrusion]]; a [[tenon]] in a [[mortise]] and tenon [[carpentry]] [[join]]}}

subSections.title: Usage notes
subSections.text: The {{m|en|tenon}} sense is sometimes spelled {{l|ja|柄}}. This alternate character might be considered by some to be a misspelling. Note that the right-hand element of {{l|ja|枘}} is {{l|ja|内}} without a top bar, while the right-hand element of {{l|ja|柄}} is {{l|ja|丙}} with a top bar.
